// 1. Package has "exports" that don't match your import
// Check node_modules/my-package/package.json "exports" field

// 2. Package only ships CJS but you're in ESM context
// The package has "main" but no "exports" with "import" condition

// 3. Monorepo workspace package not properly linked
// Fix: run npm install or yarn install to create symlinks

// 4. package.json "main" points to nonexistent file
